      <body>
         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1915-05-06">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1915-05-06">6/5</date> Vm. Burgth.; bei <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45503" ref="#person_20714"><surname>Thimig</surname></rs>. Über Titel, Besetzung, Reihenfolge, Termin. 
Wir einigen uns vorläufig auf „<rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_8120">Komoedie der Worte</rs>“; <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45504" ref="#person_21059"><surname>Walden</surname></rs> die 3 
<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45505" ref="#person_13457"><surname>Bassermannrollen</surname></rs>, Mitte October;― <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45506" ref="#person_18020"><roleName>Frl.</roleName> <surname>Mayer</surname></rs> ― (<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45507"><forename>Klara</forename></rs>),― <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45508" ref="#person_18035"><roleName>Fr.</roleName> <surname>Medelsky</surname></rs> 
(<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45509"><forename>Sophie</forename></rs>), <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45510" ref="#person_21423"><roleName>Frl.</roleName> <surname>Wohlgemuth</surname></rs> (<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45511"><forename>Agnes</forename></rs>).―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nm. am <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_8121">Fliederb.</rs> (4. A. quasi zu Ende.―) 
<rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45512"><roleName>Hr.</roleName> <roleName>Frau</roleName> <surname>Steiner</surname></rs>. Er ist bei der Musterung freigekommen.―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent"><rs type="place" xml:id="pl_09350" ref="#place_389962c9dec540ab28d04517e82c3996">Italien</rs> höchst bedenklich, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_45513" ref="#person_13222"><surname>d’Annunzios</surname></rs> Rede.</p>
         </div>
